overview.text: The Ukrainian affiliate marketing market has shown significant progress in 2025. A lot of new projects have appeared, we have seen rises and falls, many top collaborations and new formats of work. Therefore, our task is to recognize everyone who contributed to the development of the industry.
overview.remark: But of course, the opportunity to choose the best in their fields is given to you.
